title: home
text:
Hello,
Agency: A series of articles and notes stemming from the central question “What is Agency?”. Articles: * Meaning: A dedicated series to the question “What is meaning?”.
* Intelligence: Thinking about Intelligence from an AI/ML perspective, some informal reviews on latest developments.
* Other: Articles & writings on other topics with a different tone. Experiments: Some computational experiments. Notebooks: Explanations and technical notes Thoughts: Short entries with unstructured and loose thoughts. Resource Tree: Pointers and pins, an index to my current mind map of ideas and references. The purpose is dynamic, as I use the tree of information and links to share as a conversation propeller and contextual mapping to enrich dialogs.
